        <mxCell id="-4gnWyPn8esLxgZOmn1w-12" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;fontSize=16;" value="PRIVACY&lt;br&gt;Everyone can see each others:&lt;br&gt;- Approximate similarity with their own taste vector&lt;br&gt;- Can&#39;t see their real IP&lt;div&gt;-Can know that they are using a VPN&lt;br&gt;- Timing metadata still present&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Deanonymizing a user becomes non trivial. &lt;br&gt;Tracking a user&#39;s taste is possible after overtime observation&lt;br&gt;Tracking a user is easy because they have the same IP&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
